transcription.text:

Speaker 2: Yeah, this is about the third person I've spoken to.

Speaker 2: Let me get your phone number so I can pull up your account and see what's going on.

Speaker 1: Yes, please. Your phone number that you're connected to.

Speaker 1: Let me do this.

Speaker 2: No.

Speaker 1: No, I got you. I heard you say it. I'm just telling you what I'm looking at.

Speaker 1: Okay. First of all, let me go ahead and do that for you to make you right on that.

Speaker 2: All right. Give me one second to do that.

Speaker 1: I appreciate that.

Speaker 2: No problem. No problem at all, man.

Speaker 1: Like I said, the first thing you mentioned is you thought it was a scam, and that's the last thing we are.

Speaker 2: And I'm going to prove that to you.

Speaker 1: By the time you hang up, you're going to be more than happy with what we're dealing with.

Speaker 2: All right.

Speaker 1: So as of right now, I just went ahead and I refunded you that last order that you just received for that 63.95.

Speaker 2: All right.

Speaker 1: See, so it's going pretty smooth so far, right, what we're talking about.

Speaker 2: Now, what I do also see, Dennis, I noticed that when you placed your original order, you must have did it online.

Speaker 1: Is that correct, when you placed your order?

Speaker 2: Correct.

Speaker 1: Did you go online?

Speaker 2: Correct.

Speaker 1: And I'm going to tell you something else.

Speaker 2: Is that also correct, when you did the order?

Speaker 1: I guess.

Speaker 2: I have no idea, really.

Speaker 1: Yeah, because you did.

Speaker 2: You just got the regular Geneg Viagra.

Speaker 1: What I want to do for you for absolutely free, I want to send you 10 of the replacers, what I think you should have gotten in the first place.

Speaker 2: That's why I went ahead and gave you your 63.95 back for that other order.

Speaker 1: I just removed this other prescription that you had out there.

Speaker 2: I stopped those monthly shipments.

Speaker 1: I stopped those monthly refills.

Speaker 2: And I also stopped the monthly charges that was occurring with your other prescription.

Speaker 1: Now, what I want to do absolutely for free, I'm going to send you out 10 of what I think you should have got, which was the AGB.

Speaker 2: And I'm going to send you 10 of them to replace those first 10 that you got that you said didn't work for you.

Speaker 1: And I guarantee you, once you try these, you're going to want to order some more of these in the future.

Speaker 2: But what I'm going to tell you is when you do want to order, don't go online.

Speaker 1: Just do what you're doing now and give us a call.

Speaker 2: Now, I'm not going to have you on a monthly prescription like these was before.

Speaker 1: I'm going to allow you to order when you want to as far as that's concerned.

Speaker 2: So I'm going to pause all future subscriptions off that you're not getting.

Speaker 1: I'm going to change it to what I'm going to send you now.

Speaker 2: Let me tell you what I'm going to send you for free now.

Speaker 1: It's going to be a white-shaped diamond Viagra pill.

Speaker 2: It's going to have the number 100 on the back.

Speaker 1: That's the new and improved Viagra.

Speaker 2: Once you try that one, I guarantee you're going to absolutely love it,

Speaker 1: and you're going to want 10 more as soon as you get through with those.

Speaker 2: So how does that sound so far, Dennis?

Speaker 1: I appreciate that.

Speaker 2: But going forward, then I don't owe any money, right?

Speaker 1: No, no, not at all.

Speaker 2: I'm sending you 10 for free, and I'm going to change the subscription to be what I'm sending you next.

Speaker 1: So when you do order, don't go online.

Speaker 2: Listen to me very clearly.

Speaker 1: Call us like you're calling now to place another order of the ones you're going to enjoy.

Speaker 2: Okay?

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: What's your name?

Speaker 1: Because you've been of great help.

Speaker 2: Thank you.

Speaker 1: No problem.

Speaker 2: My name is Jimmy.

Speaker 1: You can call and ask for me, Dennis, when you want to order again.

Speaker 2: And remember, like I said, the pills are going to look very similar,

Speaker 1: but the ones I'm sending you are going to have that number 100 on the back,

Speaker 2: and you're going to see a drastic difference on how these work compared to what you got at first.

Speaker 1: Okay?

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: Jimmy, thank you.

Speaker 2: I really do.

Speaker 1: Not a problem.

Speaker 2: You should see the credit on your card within a couple of days, too, for that order you just received.

Speaker 1: All right?

Speaker 2: Thanks so much.

Speaker 1: Not a problem, sir.

Speaker 2: You have a great day.

Speaker 1: You too.

Speaker 2: Thanks.
